2. CNAME (Canonical Name)

Maps domain â†’ another domain:

api.myapp.com â†’ myapp-alb-123.aws.com


â— You cannot create a CNAME for the root domain (example.com).

3. Alias Record (AWS only)

Alias = CNAME but:

